impl FromSql<Text, Pg> for *const str

The returned pointer is only valid for the lifetime to the argument of from_sql. This impl is intended for uses where you want to write a new impl in terms of String, but dont want to allocate. We have to return a raw pointer instead of a reference with a lifetime due to the structure of FromSql
